title: You Won't Solve Weightloss by Saying "I Can't"
itunes:title: You Won't Solve Weightloss by Saying "I Can't"
description:
If you find yourself starting a lot of your sentences with "I can't" then listen up.
 
Today we talk about why you lead with "I can't" and how to look beyond your weightloss problems and toward your weightloss solutions.
 
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
